{"tid":1188474,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點解宜家香港人可以咁撚扭曲","createTime":"2019-06-06T09:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T08:08:35.000Z","uid":137291,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ed94f2819e40f95026d2df5267102469975b7a","tid":1188474,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母頭先睇隔離垃圾食環同埋警犬恰鳩呀怕個po<br />\n已經睇到好撚心up好撚想啲食環同埋警犬快撚啲死<br />\n跟住點解有人仲可以咁樣講嘢落井下石<br />\n仲要有壓倒性嘅正評<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCUgpyU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCUgpyU.jpg&h=34409d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解你班垃圾連登仔可以講嘢咁不負責任<br />\n有冇用過腦去諗先講嘢?<br />\n之前連登先害死咗一個女仔點解你地仲可以亂講嘢<br />\n仲要你地咁講嘢就係你班垃圾造就咗食環呢啲走狗<br />\n鬼唔望你地第時老咗啲仔女都係咁話你跟住唔撚照顧你地<br />\n香港究竟變咗咩樣"},{"pid":"231c9c999aaf8f953ad312e081edf65a444e8f10","tid":1188474,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:37:18.000Z","msg":"你諗清楚先<br />\n諗唔掂就返入你個廁所啦"},{"pid":"6039f2e484750c64d21decb13b50d6807231e2b3","tid":1188474,"uid":255105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:56:55.000Z","msg":"條友三毛黎，帶風向想香港人鬥香港人，幫食環狗同黑警開脫"},{"pid":"5ae70204721726d3ae5ab3b095695f8501551fb2","tid":1188474,"uid":194403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"人性本惡"},{"pid":"c2d358f6fd5bf8d8a598f7903e185ecd20f2997d","tid":1188474,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"9ca90d95e7a476ed7505b7cd30c2818c4746bc19","tid":1188474,"uid":32527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"人治社會岩你<br />\n呀伯犯法唔洗理<br />\n我老左都去打劫算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba90c133ff495345175645e687e129aada237e8","tid":1188474,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ca90d95e7a476ed7505b7cd30c2818